  <main>
    <h2 style="font-size: 35px; text-align: center; color: #00a7cc ">Water Parameters</h2>
    <section>
      <h3>EC</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Minimum: 0.5 dS/m</li>
        <li>Maximum: 5.0 dS/m</li>
        <li>Note: Indicates ion concentration and impacts process operations.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>SG</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Minimum: 1.000</li>
        <li>Maximum: 1.200</li>
        <li>Note:  Reflects density and impacts process calculations..</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h3>Salinity</h3>
      <ul>
      <li>Minimum: 0.1 g/L</li>
      <li>Maximum: 35.0 g/L (parts per thousand)</li>
      <li>Note: Affects corrosion and scaling potential..</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h3>ORP</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Minimum: -100 mV</li>
        <li>Maximum: 1000 mV</li>
        <li>Note: Measures the water’s ability to oxidize or reduce substances.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>TDS</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Minimum: 500 mg/L (ppm)</li>
        <li>Maximum: 2000 mg/L (ppm)</li>
        <li>Note:  Affects process efficiency and equipment performance.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>pH</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Minimum: 4.0</li>
        <li>Maximum: 10.0</li>
        <li>Note:  Affects chemical reactions and equipment longevity.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Temperature</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Minimum: 5°C</li>
        <li>Maximum: 60°C</li>
        <li>Note: Influences reaction rates and system efficiency.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
